{
  "schemaVersion": 1,
  "description": "Single source of truth for the SDK's quality tasks: which check_*.py gates exist, whether each is a hard CI gate or informational, and which profiles (quick/pr/full/release) run it. check_quality_registry.py keeps it == scripts/check_*.py on disk. Additive-only within schemaVersion 1.",
